### \[EN] SECTION 4 — Risks, Decisions, Trade-offs

* **Risks**: large families (long calls), version races, Salesforce backlog.
* **Decisions**: single-call orchestration with chunks; work table for resume; single outbound queue; “current approved” gate.
* **Trade-offs**: simpler runtime (no internal events) vs implementing 202 + resume flow; many short transactions vs progress bookkeeping.

